1.title: Aidra's Meets Her Psychic Mike
1.plot: Psychic Cab is a half-hour series that takes their audience on a fun transformation that is compelling, inspirational, and highly entertaining ride.Meet Aidra. Fun, easy going and beautiful, she has a lot of issues with men and one in particular. Her friend Mark called us and asked us to give them a lift and our psychic Mike is going to dig deep into his cards and psychic abilities and we'll get to the bottom of what is holding her back.
